------------------------------------------------------------
-- Open Questions
------------------------------------------------------------

open_question "Clojure state model: atoms per component vs single TUI atom vs statechart?  Statechart preferred per project Engine principle."
open_question "Thread model: should rendering happen on a dedicated thread or rely on core.async?  The JS version defers to nextTick."
open_question "VirtualTerminal for tests: use a Clojure in-memory byte-buffer or wrap @xterm/headless via GraalVM/nREPL?"
open_question "Image support (Kitty/iTerm2 protocols): include in initial implementation or defer?"
open_question "Windows VT input (koffi workaround in TS): skip entirely for the Clojure JVM target?"
open_question "Keybinding configuration: use EDN map analogous to EditorKeybindingsConfig; which namespace to own it?"
